{"tid":720542,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［化妝界KOL］美妝教主！南韓愛妻門將趙賢祐貪靚過女人!","createTime":"2018-06-28T03:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T06:52:43.000Z","uid":49388,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"35c680f4039faf30805806e99c0ae4153b725134","tid":720542,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180623/photo/bkn-20180623160033084-0623_00882_001_01p.jpg?20180626161148\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180623%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180623160033084-0623_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20180626161148&h=b16e2457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南韓上輪世盃分組賽對瑞典飲恨0比1，不過佢哋個高大龍門趙賢祐就勁搶鏡，唔單止多次救出危險射門，「白到可以反光」嘅俊臉亦成為網民熱話，唔少人覺得趙賢祐Oppa係化咗妝先落場，紛紛留言問佢「邊度買粉底？」帶挈呢位「大邱迪基亞」嘅IG突然多咗幾千個粉絲！<br />\n<br />\n依家26歲嘅趙賢祐大器晚成，22歲先至進軍韓職踢FC大邱，到依家仍然效力呢支球隊，不過擁有1米89身高嘅佢潛力優厚，對高空波有強大控制力之外，應付下三流攻門都唔差，所以深受領隊重用。趙賢祐曾表示南韓傳奇門將李雲在係佢偶像，因為睇過佢喺02年世界盃帶領南韓殺入4強，所以就立志要做一個足球員。<br />\n<br />\n雖然南韓今晚對墨西哥，可能會改派速度快嘅金承奎把關，不過趙賢祐嘅「白面」仍然係熱門話題，有傳話佢操得太勁搞到「面都白晒」，但查實趙賢祐除咗天生麗質，本身亦非常貪靚，經常敷面膜保養白滑皮膚，比好多女人更加貪靚！<br />\n<br />\n趙賢祐今屆世盃一戰爆紅，不過女粉絲們唔好再FF，事關佢已經成家立室，而且仲係超級「愛妻號」！趙賢祐手臂上紋咗靚靚老婆個樣，社交網亦狂Po家庭照同囡囡成長記，佢喺IG個自我介紹入面就寫住「Lee Hee Young的老公，Ha Rin的爸爸」，喺最愛嘅家人面前，「老公」同「爸爸」先係佢最引以為榮嘅身份。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180623/photo/bkn-20180623160033084-0623_00882_001_06p.jpg?20180626161148\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180623%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180623160033084-0623_00882_001_06p.jpg%3F20180626161148&h=80761320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180623/photo/bkn-20180623160033084-0623_00882_001_04p.jpg?20180626161148\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180623%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180623160033084-0623_00882_001_04p.jpg%3F20180626161148&h=594ddf2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180623/photo/bkn-20180623160033084-0623_00882_001_05p.jpg?20180626161148\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180623%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180623160033084-0623_00882_001_05p.jpg%3F20180626161148&h=d868ba08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180623/photo/bkn-20180623160033084-0623_00882_001_03p.jpg?20180626161148\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180623%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180623160033084-0623_00882_001_03p.jpg%3F20180626161148&h=6855e858&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8740b7e3b5c454fa54320e792793ea62cdad9d7","tid":720542,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:46:38.000Z","msg":"條女典型整容樣"},{"pid":"4b20631dd5ae85b31253d9abccc6cf98e239391c","tid":720542,"uid":161731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:48:38.000Z","msg":"見到佢就諗起笑波子"},{"pid":"32a0321d4b1735129f7b8551615c4ca4404a0b9f","tid":720542,"uid":161731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8740b7e3b5c454fa54320e792793ea62cdad9d7","tid":720542,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:46:38.000Z","msg":"條女典型整容樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T03:48:55.000Z","msg":"蓋ching lunch 食咩"},{"pid":"1e62c873cc8ab2255d92c9507340348949f6b58a","tid":720542,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T04:12:53.000Z","msg":"其實佢係顏值一般版趙權"},{"pid":"f76d872739bcaaf6e82a3660811bc2c9288de182","tid":720542,"uid":19126,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T04:22:40.000Z","msg":"下三流攻門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下三路下話文盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4164b8b5b02268507911294b4a3913f268410f90","tid":720542,"uid